    "title": "Urgent Opening Real Estate Agent at Oberoi Mall",
    "description": "Oberoi Mall, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Real Estate Agent for our Pune operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Oberoi Mall:\nOberoi Mall is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Client Relationship Management\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Learning & development budget\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Oberoi Mall!",
